{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/2024-07-19/thenextjs-week-8/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a11349473b64b66a174a11fd17f7a7ae/fb816/thenextjs-week-8-cover.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a11349473b64b66a174a11fd17f7a7ae/a59e9/thenextjs-week-8-cover.webp 192w,\n/static/a11349473b64b66a174a11fd17f7a7ae/0ca9f/thenextjs-week-8-cover.webp 384w,\n/static/a11349473b64b66a174a11fd17f7a7ae/dc9b9/thenextjs-week-8-cover.webp 768w,\n/static/a11349473b64b66a174a11fd17f7a7ae/a6361/thenextjs-week-8-cover.webp 960w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a11349473b64b66a174a11fd17f7a7ae/150b2/thenextjs-week-8-cover.jpg 192w,\n/static/a11349473b64b66a174a11fd17f7a7ae/6985d/thenextjs-week-8-cover.jpg 384w,\n/static/a11349473b64b66a174a11fd17f7a7ae/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-cover.jpg 768w,\n/static/a11349473b64b66a174a11fd17f7a7ae/fb816/thenextjs-week-8-cover.jpg 960w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a11349473b64b66a174a11fd17f7a7ae/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-cover.jpg\"\n            alt=\"프로젝트 다섯째주 회고\"\n            title=\"프로젝트 다섯째주 회고\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"8주차\" style=\"position:relative;\">8주차<a href=\"#8%EC%A3%BC%EC%B0%A8\" aria-label=\"8주차 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h1>\n<p><strong>이번 주 to-do</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" checked disabled> Vercel을 통해 1차 테스트 배포</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" checked disabled> 1차 UI Test 후 이슈 수정 및 리팩토링</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" checked disabled> 반응형 추가 (~)</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" checked disabled> 페이지별로 필요한 API 정의 문서화</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" checked disabled> 기능 구현 (~)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"what-we-mainly-did\" style=\"position:relative;\">What we mainly did<a href=\"#what-we-mainly-did\" aria-label=\"what we mainly did permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"vercel---build-and-deployment\" style=\"position:relative;\">Vercel - build and deployment<a href=\"#vercel---build-and-deployment\" aria-label=\"vercel   build and deployment permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://callmebyneon.github.io/2024-06-15/thenextjs-week-3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">저번에</a> 작성했던 next-auth 테스트 코드를 vercel로 배포해 보면서 라우트 되지 않는 라우트 그룹 아래의 page.tsx는 빌드 오류가 발생시켜 초기 빌드 시 예측하지 못하는 빌드 에러가 발생할 것을 예상하여 이번 주에는 1차 테스트 빌드를 진행해 봤다. 그리고 역시나 많은 빌드 에러를 마주하게 됐다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"trouble-shooting\" style=\"position:relative;\">Trouble shooting<a href=\"#trouble-shooting\" aria-label=\"trouble shooting permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>🔗 <a href=\"https://github.com/woongteco/nextcamp-12t/issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aclosed+label%3Alog\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">마주했던 빌드 오류 Repository/Issue에 정리</a></li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>Next.js Middleware에서의 세션 확인을 통한 접근 제한하기</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c8cac9f426c18477ceaef0d33ec2ca2b/736b0/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c8cac9f426c18477ceaef0d33ec2ca2b/a59e9/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-1.webp 192w,\n/static/c8cac9f426c18477ceaef0d33ec2ca2b/0ca9f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-1.webp 384w,\n/static/c8cac9f426c18477ceaef0d33ec2ca2b/dc9b9/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-1.webp 768w,\n/static/c8cac9f426c18477ceaef0d33ec2ca2b/9fa0d/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-1.webp 963w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c8cac9f426c18477ceaef0d33ec2ca2b/150b2/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-1.jpg 192w,\n/static/c8cac9f426c18477ceaef0d33ec2ca2b/6985d/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-1.jpg 384w,\n/static/c8cac9f426c18477ceaef0d33ec2ca2b/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-1.jpg 768w,\n/static/c8cac9f426c18477ceaef0d33ec2ca2b/736b0/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-1.jpg 963w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c8cac9f426c18477ceaef0d33ec2ca2b/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-1.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Error: Dynamic Code Evaluation not allowed in Edge Runtime\"\n            title=\"Error: Dynamic Code Evaluation not allowed in Edge Runtime\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<details>\r\n  <summary>(참고) 관련 패키지 버전</summary>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>mongoose: \"^8.5.0\"</li>\r\n    <li>next: \"14.2.4\"</li>\r\n    <li>next-auth: \"^5.0.0-beta.19\"</li>\r\n    <li>react: \"^18\"</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n</details>\n<p>사실상 이번 테스트 배포에서 최종 보스 같은 오류였다. 이게 게임이었다면 가장 먼저 만난 녀석이 가장 최약체였겠지만.. 이 오류는 그렇지 않았다.</p>\n<p>빌드 당시 마이페이지와 글 작성 페이지는 로그인한 사용자만 접근할 수 있도록 미들웨어에서 NextAuth를 사용한 리턴 오브젝트의 auth를 사용하여 세션을 확인하고 그 값에 따라 matcher로 접근을 제한하도록 하고 있었다.</p>\n<p>정확히 어느 부분 때문에 오류가 나는지 찾을 수가 없어 헤매던 중 <a href=\"https://velog.io/@sun1301/FDBS-How-to-deploy#2-dynamic-code-evaluation-e-g-eval-new-function-webassemblycompile-not-allowed-in-edge-runtime\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">미들웨어에서 getSession을 사용하여 에러가 발생할 수 있다는 글</a>을 발견했다. 이 글을 보고 auth 함수를 이용하여 session 확인 후 접근 제한하는 코드를 미들웨어에서 layout.tsx와 page.tsx로 옮겼더니 더 이상 같은 오류를 볼 수 없었다.</p>\n<figure>\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/e5c7f/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 32.29166666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/a59e9/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.webp 192w,\n/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/0ca9f/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.webp 384w,\n/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/dc9b9/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.webp 768w,\n/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/e2c2f/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.webp 1152w,\n/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/f3efb/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.webp 1536w,\n/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/28300/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.webp 1839w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/150b2/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.jpg 192w,\n/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/6985d/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.jpg 384w,\n/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.jpg 768w,\n/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/4472f/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.jpg 1152w,\n/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/d58d1/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.jpg 1536w,\n/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/e5c7f/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.jpg 1839w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/jpeg\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/15ce35c77095f61f2c83db4e01439990/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-1-diff.jpg\" alt=\"빌드 문제로 변경했던 미들웨어 코드, auth as getSession하여 사용한 점 참고\" title=\"빌드 문제로 변경했던 미들웨어 코드, auth as getSession하여 사용한 점 참고\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<figcaption>빌드 문제로 변경했던 미들웨어 코드, `export { auth as getSession }`하여 사용한 점 참고</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>이전 코드가 로컬에서 실행해 봤을 때야 잘 동작하는 것 같았지만 <a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/app/building-your-application/authentication#session-management\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Next.js 문서</a>를 보니 직접 auth 함수를 사용하지 않고 쿠키 기반으로 세션을 확인하는 방법을 소개하고 있었다.</p>\n<p>하지만 auth 함수의 설명을 언뜻 읽어보면 미들웨어 함수에서 그냥 사용하면 되는 것처럼 느껴진다. <a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/app/building-your-application/routing/middleware#runtime\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Next.js 문서</a>에서는 미들웨어가 현재(v13.1.0 이후) Edge 런타임만 지원하고 Node.js 런타임을 사용할 수 없다고 설명하고 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8ee350285db73b6ffca698dbd3a3bbf9/c9272/thenextjs-week-8-1-about-auth.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 17.1875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/8ee350285db73b6ffca698dbd3a3bbf9/a59e9/thenextjs-week-8-1-about-auth.webp 192w,\n/static/8ee350285db73b6ffca698dbd3a3bbf9/0ca9f/thenextjs-week-8-1-about-auth.webp 384w,\n/static/8ee350285db73b6ffca698dbd3a3bbf9/dc9b9/thenextjs-week-8-1-about-auth.webp 768w,\n/static/8ee350285db73b6ffca698dbd3a3bbf9/e2c2f/thenextjs-week-8-1-about-auth.webp 1152w,\n/static/8ee350285db73b6ffca698dbd3a3bbf9/9f431/thenextjs-week-8-1-about-auth.webp 1234w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/8ee350285db73b6ffca698dbd3a3bbf9/150b2/thenextjs-week-8-1-about-auth.jpg 192w,\n/static/8ee350285db73b6ffca698dbd3a3bbf9/6985d/thenextjs-week-8-1-about-auth.jpg 384w,\n/static/8ee350285db73b6ffca698dbd3a3bbf9/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-1-about-auth.jpg 768w,\n/static/8ee350285db73b6ffca698dbd3a3bbf9/4472f/thenextjs-week-8-1-about-auth.jpg 1152w,\n/static/8ee350285db73b6ffca698dbd3a3bbf9/c9272/thenextjs-week-8-1-about-auth.jpg 1234w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/8ee350285db73b6ffca698dbd3a3bbf9/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-1-about-auth.jpg\"\n            alt=\"NextAuthResult의 auth 함수 설명\"\n            title=\"NextAuthResult의 auth 함수 설명\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Next.js 앱에서 NextAuth.js와 상호작용하는 보편적인 방법입니다. auth.ts에서 NextAuth.js를 초기화한 후 미들웨어, 서버 컴포넌트, 라우트 핸들러들(app/), Edge 또는 Node.js API 경로 (page/)에서 이 방법을 사용합니다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>음… 미들웨어의 기본 설명에 대해서도 다시 한 번 살펴본다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Middleware allows you to run code before a request is completed. Then, based on the incoming request, you can modify the response by rewriting, redirecting, modifying the request or response headers, or responding directly.<br>\n미들웨어를 사용하면 요청이 완료되기 전에 코드를 실행할 수 있습니다. 그런 다음 들어오는 요청에 따라 요청 또는 응답 헤더를 다시 작성, 리디렉션, 수정하거나 직접 응답하여 응답을 수정할 수 있습니다.<br>\n출처: <a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/app/building-your-application/routing/middleware\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://nextjs.org/docs/app/building-your-application/routing/middleware</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>미들웨어는 결국 페이지 요청이 완료되기 전에 실행하기 위한 코드를 적게 되는데, 이 부분은 아직 Next와 Next의 미들웨어에 대한 이해가 확실하지 않다 보니 너무 두루뭉술하게만 해결하고 넘어가는 느낌이긴 하다. 더 공부가 필요해 보인다.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>리액트 코드 작성 시 주의가 필요한 부분들</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dbd5c57820b2ba9be6f03992cc8330a5/d4d39/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-key-prop.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.229166666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/dbd5c57820b2ba9be6f03992cc8330a5/a59e9/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-key-prop.webp 192w,\n/static/dbd5c57820b2ba9be6f03992cc8330a5/0ca9f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-key-prop.webp 384w,\n/static/dbd5c57820b2ba9be6f03992cc8330a5/dc9b9/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-key-prop.webp 768w,\n/static/dbd5c57820b2ba9be6f03992cc8330a5/e2c2f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-key-prop.webp 1152w,\n/static/dbd5c57820b2ba9be6f03992cc8330a5/f6e5b/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-key-prop.webp 1193w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/dbd5c57820b2ba9be6f03992cc8330a5/150b2/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-key-prop.jpg 192w,\n/static/dbd5c57820b2ba9be6f03992cc8330a5/6985d/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-key-prop.jpg 384w,\n/static/dbd5c57820b2ba9be6f03992cc8330a5/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-key-prop.jpg 768w,\n/static/dbd5c57820b2ba9be6f03992cc8330a5/4472f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-key-prop.jpg 1152w,\n/static/dbd5c57820b2ba9be6f03992cc8330a5/d4d39/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-key-prop.jpg 1193w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/dbd5c57820b2ba9be6f03992cc8330a5/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-key-prop.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Error: Missing &quot;key&quot; prop for element in iterator react/jsx-key\"\n            title=\"Error: Missing &quot;key&quot; prop for element in iterator react/jsx-key\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Missing “key” prop</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://callmebyneon.github.io/2022-06-21/not-unique-key-in-react/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">이전에 unique key prop에 대해 블로그 글을 작성</a>하기도 했지만, JSX에서 Array.map을 이용하여 Element 렌더링 시 key prop이 아예 존재하지 않을 때 빌드 시 오류가 발생했다. 물론 unique 한 key 값이 아닌 경우에 로컬 환경(<code>npm run dev</code>)에서 경고 콘솔을 표시하니 주의한다.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ko.legacy.reactjs.org/docs/lists-and-keys.html#keys\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">참고한 내용</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/339353bda71cf93f7a42fec99878993e/d1ce2/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-displayName.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 22.916666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/339353bda71cf93f7a42fec99878993e/a59e9/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-displayName.webp 192w,\n/static/339353bda71cf93f7a42fec99878993e/0ca9f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-displayName.webp 384w,\n/static/339353bda71cf93f7a42fec99878993e/dc9b9/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-displayName.webp 768w,\n/static/339353bda71cf93f7a42fec99878993e/e2c2f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-displayName.webp 1152w,\n/static/339353bda71cf93f7a42fec99878993e/661f4/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-displayName.webp 1199w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/339353bda71cf93f7a42fec99878993e/150b2/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-displayName.jpg 192w,\n/static/339353bda71cf93f7a42fec99878993e/6985d/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-displayName.jpg 384w,\n/static/339353bda71cf93f7a42fec99878993e/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-displayName.jpg 768w,\n/static/339353bda71cf93f7a42fec99878993e/4472f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-displayName.jpg 1152w,\n/static/339353bda71cf93f7a42fec99878993e/d1ce2/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-displayName.jpg 1199w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/339353bda71cf93f7a42fec99878993e/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-displayName.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Error: Component definition is missing display name  react/display-name\"\n            title=\"Error: Component definition is missing display name  react/display-name\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Missing displayName in componnet definition</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><code>React.forwardRef</code> 사용 시 displayName을 따로 지정하지 않으면 리액트는 이름이 없는 컴포넌트로 해석하기 때문에 변수명과 별개로 <code>ModalPortal.displayName = \"ModalPortal\"</code>과같이 displayName을 지정해야 한다.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://velog.io/@jellyjw/React%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-forwardRef-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%96%88%EC%9D%84-%EB%95%8C-displayName-error-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">참고한 내용</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8720cebf36fa19aeaff1851d14881551/1060f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-hook.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 7.8125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/8720cebf36fa19aeaff1851d14881551/a59e9/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-hook.webp 192w,\n/static/8720cebf36fa19aeaff1851d14881551/0ca9f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-hook.webp 384w,\n/static/8720cebf36fa19aeaff1851d14881551/dc9b9/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-hook.webp 768w,\n/static/8720cebf36fa19aeaff1851d14881551/e2c2f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-hook.webp 1152w,\n/static/8720cebf36fa19aeaff1851d14881551/8866f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-hook.webp 1181w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/8720cebf36fa19aeaff1851d14881551/150b2/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-hook.jpg 192w,\n/static/8720cebf36fa19aeaff1851d14881551/6985d/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-hook.jpg 384w,\n/static/8720cebf36fa19aeaff1851d14881551/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-hook.jpg 768w,\n/static/8720cebf36fa19aeaff1851d14881551/4472f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-hook.jpg 1152w,\n/static/8720cebf36fa19aeaff1851d14881551/1060f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-hook.jpg 1181w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/8720cebf36fa19aeaff1851d14881551/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-2-hook.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Error: React Hook &quot;useId&quot; id called conditionally. React Hooks must be called in the exact same order in every component render. react-hooks/rules-of-hooks\"\n            title=\"Error: React Hook &quot;useId&quot; id called conditionally. React Hooks must be called in the exact same order in every component render. react-hooks/rules-of-hooks\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>React Hook must be called not conditionally</strong>\n<ul>\n<li>리액트 훅은 훅이 사용된 컴포넌트가 렌더 될 때마다 항상 똑같이 실행되어야 하기 때문에 if 문 블록 안이나 if 문을 사용한 이후에 사용할 수 없다.</li>\n<li>이 경우에는 <code>useId</code>를 사용할 때 <code>const uniqueId = id || useId()</code>와 같이 id prop을 받지 않을 때 useId를 바로 이용하여 uniqueId에 값을 저장하도록 작성했던 코드가 문제였다. 이런 경우의 훅 사용도 로컬 환경(<code>npm run dev</code>) 실행에서는 문제가 없어 보였지만 빌드 과정에서 오류가 발생해 빌드가 중단되었다.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://react.dev/reference/rules/rules-of-hooks\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">참고한 내용</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>ESLint와 TypeError, 경고들</li>\n</ol>\n<p>main 브랜치에 머지 하기 전 나름대로 확인 후 dev 브랜치를 main에 머지 했지만 빌드 오류를 통해 이전에 발견하지 못했던 TypeError도 발견하고 ESLint로 인해 빌드에 실패한 경우도 마주쳤다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1be755a05db5b2533caf98f785e15189/d4d39/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-3-eslint.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 7.8125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/1be755a05db5b2533caf98f785e15189/a59e9/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-3-eslint.webp 192w,\n/static/1be755a05db5b2533caf98f785e15189/0ca9f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-3-eslint.webp 384w,\n/static/1be755a05db5b2533caf98f785e15189/dc9b9/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-3-eslint.webp 768w,\n/static/1be755a05db5b2533caf98f785e15189/e2c2f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-3-eslint.webp 1152w,\n/static/1be755a05db5b2533caf98f785e15189/f6e5b/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-3-eslint.webp 1193w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/1be755a05db5b2533caf98f785e15189/150b2/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-3-eslint.jpg 192w,\n/static/1be755a05db5b2533caf98f785e15189/6985d/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-3-eslint.jpg 384w,\n/static/1be755a05db5b2533caf98f785e15189/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-3-eslint.jpg 768w,\n/static/1be755a05db5b2533caf98f785e15189/4472f/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-3-eslint.jpg 1152w,\n/static/1be755a05db5b2533caf98f785e15189/d4d39/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-3-eslint.jpg 1193w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/1be755a05db5b2533caf98f785e15189/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-build-error-3-eslint.jpg\"\n            alt=\"Error: &#39; can be escaped with &#39;, ‘, &#39;, ’. react/np-unescaped-entities\"\n            title=\"Error: &#39; can be escaped with &#39;, ‘, &#39;, ’. react/np-unescaped-entities\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>ESLint 오류 같은 경우, ESLint의 권장되는 규칙 중 <a href=\"https://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-react/blob/master/docs/rules/no-unescaped-entities.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">no-unescaped-entities</a>가 있었다. 이 규칙은 ESLint에서 따옴표(<code>\"\"</code>) 혹은 less-than-sign/greater-than-sign(<code>&#x3C;></code>)와 같은 문자열은 html이나 jsx와 같은 마크업 문법과 혼동되기 쉬우니 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/wiki/Common_HTML_entities_used_for_typography\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">html entities</a> 사용(예: <code>&#x3C;</code> → <code>&#x26;lt;</code>)을 권장한다. 물론 ESLint 설정에서 사용하지 않도록 수정할 수도 있겠지만 권장되는 내용대로 html entities로 변경해 주었다.</p>\n<p>TypeError 역시 로컬 환경에서는 오류로 인식되지 않아 화면에 렌더링 되는 데에 지장을 주지 않았지만 빌드 과정에서 오류를 발생시켰다.</p>\n<p>이러한 오류들 이외에도 경고 로그도 확인할 수 있었는데, 대표적으로는 <code>&#x3C;Image></code> 요소(Element)는 반드시 alt 속성을 가져야 하는데 가지고 있지 않아 발생한 경고였다. 이런 문제는 접근성 측면에서도 좋지 않기 때문에 고쳐주었다.</p>\n<p>로컬 환경에서 확인하지 못했던 이유로 빌드 오류를 여러 번 마주하게 됐는데, 이후로 갑작스럽게 빌드 오류를 마주하지 않기 위해 1차 배포를 진행했다. 결국 배포에 성공하긴 했지만 이 정도의 고생을 또 하고 싶지는 않기 때문에 Vercel 배포로 자동으로 레포에 설치된 Vercel 깃허브 앱에서 main이 아닌 브랜치 업데이트 시 Preview 상태를 보여주는 점을 앞으로 좀 활용해 보려 한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"ui-qa-issues\" style=\"position:relative;\">UI QA Issues<a href=\"#ui-qa-issues\" aria-label=\"ui qa issues permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>1차 QA에서는 실제 기능 중에는 로그인/회원가입 기능과 전체적인 구현도, 기본적인 화면 요소들의 동작 예상 가능성들을 먼저 볼 수밖에 없었다. 가장 큰 문제는 전체적인 레이아웃이나 리스트 그리드와 같은 기본적인 반응형도 극히 일부만 적용되어 있다는 점이었다. PC-first로 컴포넌트들을 개발하긴 했지만 헤더나 푸터, 사이드바 메뉴, 메인 검색창과 같은 부분은 반드시 반응형 스타일을 추가해야 최소한 어색하지 않아 보일듯하다.</p>\n<figure>\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 647px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/bc68be98b3f48ef5affc53a5fb5c1864/89811/thenextjs-week-8-need-responsive-layout.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 55.208333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/bc68be98b3f48ef5affc53a5fb5c1864/a59e9/thenextjs-week-8-need-responsive-layout.webp 192w,\n/static/bc68be98b3f48ef5affc53a5fb5c1864/0ca9f/thenextjs-week-8-need-responsive-layout.webp 384w,\n/static/bc68be98b3f48ef5affc53a5fb5c1864/cbdaf/thenextjs-week-8-need-responsive-layout.webp 647w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 647px) 100vw, 647px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/bc68be98b3f48ef5affc53a5fb5c1864/150b2/thenextjs-week-8-need-responsive-layout.jpg 192w,\n/static/bc68be98b3f48ef5affc53a5fb5c1864/6985d/thenextjs-week-8-need-responsive-layout.jpg 384w,\n/static/bc68be98b3f48ef5affc53a5fb5c1864/89811/thenextjs-week-8-need-responsive-layout.jpg 647w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 647px) 100vw, 647px\" type=\"image/jpeg\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/bc68be98b3f48ef5affc53a5fb5c1864/89811/thenextjs-week-8-need-responsive-layout.jpg\" alt=\"기본적으로 필요한 컴포넌트 반응형 스타일들 진행도 (6 of 19 tasks)\" title=\"기본적으로 필요한 컴포넌트 반응형 스타일들 진행도 (6 of 19 tasks)\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n  <figcaption>기본적으로 필요한 컴포넌트 반응형 스타일들 진행도 (6 of 19 tasks)</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>그 외에는 기능 개발을 많이 진행하여 배포한 것이 아니기 때문에 더미 데이터들을 따라 중구난방으로 통일되지 않고 있다. 이런 문제를 데이터 스키마를 확정하고 스키마에 따라 각 데이터 타입에 맞춰 컴포넌트들에서 상태를 보여주는 부분이 한 번 더 업데이트가 필요할 것으로 예상된다.</p>\n<p>마지막으로는 각 화면 요소들이 필요한 동작들을 정확히 구현하는 일이 조금 더 남았고, 이후에 이 동작들을 API와 연결하여 제대로 동작하는지 확인하는 과정만이 남았다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"apis\" style=\"position:relative;\">APIs<a href=\"#apis\" aria-label=\"apis permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p>일단 배포된 화면을 보면서 필요한 API들의 목록을 쭉 적어나갔다.</p>\n<figure>\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/2b19d8f1c6a133ad5e6e3562f9c80218/51f40/thenextjs-week-8-apis.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 20.833333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/2b19d8f1c6a133ad5e6e3562f9c80218/a59e9/thenextjs-week-8-apis.webp 192w,\n/static/2b19d8f1c6a133ad5e6e3562f9c80218/0ca9f/thenextjs-week-8-apis.webp 384w,\n/static/2b19d8f1c6a133ad5e6e3562f9c80218/dc9b9/thenextjs-week-8-apis.webp 768w,\n/static/2b19d8f1c6a133ad5e6e3562f9c80218/e2c2f/thenextjs-week-8-apis.webp 1152w,\n/static/2b19d8f1c6a133ad5e6e3562f9c80218/7fc30/thenextjs-week-8-apis.webp 1171w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/2b19d8f1c6a133ad5e6e3562f9c80218/150b2/thenextjs-week-8-apis.jpg 192w,\n/static/2b19d8f1c6a133ad5e6e3562f9c80218/6985d/thenextjs-week-8-apis.jpg 384w,\n/static/2b19d8f1c6a133ad5e6e3562f9c80218/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-apis.jpg 768w,\n/static/2b19d8f1c6a133ad5e6e3562f9c80218/4472f/thenextjs-week-8-apis.jpg 1152w,\n/static/2b19d8f1c6a133ad5e6e3562f9c80218/51f40/thenextjs-week-8-apis.jpg 1171w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/jpeg\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/2b19d8f1c6a133ad5e6e3562f9c80218/19de6/thenextjs-week-8-apis.jpg\" alt=\"Github Project에 정리한 구현해야 할 API 목록 초안 일부\" title=\"Github Project에 정리한 구현해야 할 API 목록 초안 일부\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n  <figcaption>Github Project에 정리한 구현해야 할 API 목록 초안 일부</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>전달받을 데이터 스키마나 URI, 쿼리 스트링들이나 더 필요한 API가 있을지는 더 팀원들과 이야기를 하며 작성 후 개발을 진행할 예정이다. 아마 개발하면서도 수정할 부분이 보이지 않을까 예상해본다 😂</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"what-we-have-done-and-have-to-do\" style=\"position:relative;\">What we have done and have to do<a href=\"#what-we-have-done-and-have-to-do\" aria-label=\"what we have done and have to do permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th>목표</th>\n<th>완료도</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1주차</td>\n<td>기획안&#x26;프로토타입 보충, 개발환경 세팅</td>\n<td>✅✅✅🔲🔲</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2주차</td>\n<td>과업 범위 정하기, 역할 분담, 마일스톤 추가, 공통 컴포넌트&#x26;라우트 정리, 페이지 마크업</td>\n<td>✅✅✅✅🔲</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3주차</td>\n<td>공통 컴포넌트 개발, 페이지 마크업&#x26;스타일링, 데이터 스키마 타입과 ERD 이해, 리팩토링 및 merge 충돌 해결</td>\n<td>✅✅✅✅</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4주차</td>\n<td>공통 컴포넌트 개발 및 리팩토링, 반응형 추가, MongoDB 구성 및 연결(+Auth.js 적용), 기능 로직 구현</td>\n<td>✅✅🔲🔲</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5주차</td>\n<td><strong>1차 테스트 배포, UI 이슈 수정 및 리팩토링, 반응형 추가, API 정의 문서화, 기능 구현</strong></td>\n<td>✅✅✅✅✅</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6주차</td>\n<td>데이터 스키마 정의, API 연결, 배포, QA/리팩토링</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7주차</td>\n<td>QA 마무리, 프로젝트 회고, 발표 준비&#x26;성과발표</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr>\n<p>본 후기는 본 후기는 [유데미x스나이퍼팩토리] 프로젝트 캠프 : Next.js 1기 과정(B-log) 리뷰로 작성 되었습니다.</p>\n<p>#유데미 #udemy #웅진씽크빅 #스나이퍼팩토리 #인사이드아웃 #미래내일일경험 #프로젝트캠프 #부트캠프 #Next.js #프론트엔드개발자양성과정 #개발자교육과정</p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    widt